These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
House: cottage, gothic-revival, colonial, tower, craftsman, townhouse, modern
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the dutch##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the colonial house is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the craftsman house##1
12. the craftsman house is the person driving the bike##1
13. the cottage house is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the german##1
16. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the modern house is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| House      | gothic-revival  | townhouse        | craftsman | colonial      | tower     | cottage      | modern     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

